## 🟡 低危建议

### 13. 依赖安全审计

**建议**:

```bash
# 添加到 package.json scripts
{
  "scripts": {
    "audit": "npm audit",
    "audit:fix": "npm audit fix",
    "outdated": "npm outdated",
    "check-deps": "ncu"
  }
}
```

```typescript
// 自动化依赖检查
import { execSync } from 'child_process';

function checkDependencyVulnerabilities() {
  try {
    const result = execSync('npm audit --json', { encoding: 'utf-8' });
    const audit = JSON.parse(result);

    if (audit.vulnerabilities && audit.vulnerabilities.length > 0) {
      const critical = audit.vulnerabilities.filter(v => v.severity === 'critical');
      if (critical.length > 0) {
        console.error(`发现 ${critical.length} 个严重漏洞！`);
        process.exit(1);
      }
    }
  } catch (error) {
    console.error('依赖审计失败');
  }
}
```

